inen. Better safe than sorry, sier n\u00e5 jeg."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8de39fc012b86a652fad2e1e6f14e25f4afdcd37670f32b69a3ce279180a72da"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2016-03-21T15:36:36.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Under halvparten av \u00e5rets russ i Trondheim har vaksinert seg mot hjernehinnebetennelse."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article12294617.ece/dobzhf/ALTERNATES/w980-default/IMG_russ.jpg_1_1_CE8LOR3.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/9eebcb78010ef90d46fa5281d8cb4f36f3b4bb1b.jpg?59707f5f"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Russen tar ikke vaksine mot hjernehinnebetennelse -adressa.no", "Ungdom spesielt utsatt", "En farlig sykdom", "- B\u00f8r vaksinere seg", "- Better safe than sorry"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "9eebcb78010ef90d46fa5281d8cb4f36f3b4bb1b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Russ", "Sykdom", "Trondheim"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Russ,Sykdom,Trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "health-and-fitness"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["vaksine", "spesielt utsatt", "safe than sorry", "russ", "hjernehinnebetennelse"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["hovedrussestyret for trondheim 2016", "trondheim 2016"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["russ", "buskerud", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["andreas tonning", "eli sagvik"]}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/nyheter/trondheim/article12294617